{"tid":2019332,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普重申不想與習近平談話　對兩國經貿協議不感興奮","createTime":"2020-05-16T08:06:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T03:21:51.000Z","uid":41404,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"032c6a6c082a9140b9bbcd764438851bdbed4dc7","tid":2019332,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T08:06:56.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普重申，目前不想與國家主席習近平對話，對於是否打算對中國加徵關稅，或者撕毀首階段貿易協議，他說不想談論這個問題。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普表示，中國正在購買很多美國商品，但當新冠病毒從中國傳入的時候，貿易協議的墨水幾乎未乾，他對協議已經不感到興奮，指某程度上失去了一些興趣。<br />\n<br />\n白宮經濟顧問庫德洛就說，首階段協議仍然生效，未有破裂，中方亦正在努力履行協議，但在購買商品的速度有點慢，認為與市場與經濟情況有關。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部日前表示，中美達成首階段經貿協議，有利中美及全世界，雙方應秉持平等與相互尊重原則，共同落實好協議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1526559-20200516.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1526559-20200516.htm&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=551116b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1526559-20200516.htm&h=f0d18419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1526559-20200516.htm</a>"},{"pid":"dea029802e419173cbde2e822d986bd84800b46f","tid":2019332,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T08:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://businessfocus.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE525.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE525.jpg&h=bd20b49d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2575000/2575664/B1B52FFA-EE7F-46AB-B7E8-18C99BD65702_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fc